Principia to Start $750 Million Asia Hedge Fund, Reuters Says

-- B y   B e i   H u
-- 
2011-05-27T10:35:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/principia-to-start-750-million-asia-hedge-fund-reuters-says.html
Principia Capital Advisors plans to
start an Asia hedge fund with more than $750 million this
summer, Reuters  reported  today, citing three unidentified people
familiar with the matter. The amount will make it the second-
biggest hedge fund startup in the region this year, the report
said.  PCA will have offices in  Hong Kong  and Beijing and begin
with commodity trading advisers, or CTA, betting on credit and
equity trends, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bei Hu in Hong Kong at 
 bhu5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andreea Papuc at 
 apapuc1@bloomberg.net  